## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="1b855-228">值永遠不會影響上次要刻度和格線的間隔位移<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffset%2A>屬性<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-228">The interval offset of minor tick marks and grid lines is never affected by the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffset%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1b855-229"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine.IntervalOffset%2A>屬性設定會定義位移的度量單位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-229">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine.IntervalOffset%2A> property setting defines the units of measurement of the offset.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1b855-230"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine.Interval%2A>可以是負數的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-230">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine.Interval%2A> can be a negative value.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1b855-231">預設值是`Auto`(`0`)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-231">The default value is `Auto` (`0`).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="1b855-232">下列程式碼範例示範三個應用程式的帶狀線。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-232">The following code example demonstrates three applications of strip lines.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1b855-233">首先，水平帶狀線會新增週期性間隔。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-233">First, horizontal strip lines are added at recurring intervals.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1b855-234">第二個、 垂直帶狀線會反白顯示週末資料點。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-234">Second, vertical strip lines are added to highlight weekend data points.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1b855-235">最後，會加入非週期性帶狀線，表示圖表的第一個數列中資料點的平均值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-235">Lastly, a non-recurring strip line is added to denote the mean of the data points in the first series of the chart.</span></span>  
  
