## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="1b855-239">根據預設，這個屬性設定為<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType.Auto>; 實際值，這個屬性由<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine.IntervalType%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-239">By default, this property is set to <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType.Auto>; the actual value of this property is determined by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine.IntervalType%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="1b855-240">下列程式碼範例示範三個應用程式的帶狀線。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-240">The following code example demonstrates three applications of strip lines.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1b855-241">首先，水平帶狀線會新增週期性間隔。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-241">First, horizontal strip lines are added at recurring intervals.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1b855-242">第二個、 垂直帶狀線會反白顯示週末資料點。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-242">Second, vertical strip lines are added to highlight weekend data points.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1b855-243">最後，會加入非週期性帶狀線，表示圖表的第一個數列中資料點的平均值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-243">Lastly, a non-recurring strip line is added to denote the mean of the data points in the first series of the chart.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
