## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="1b855-289">當這個屬性設定的值為<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.TextOrientation.Auto>，文字的方向根據圖表類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-289">When this property is set to a value of <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.TextOrientation.Auto>, the text is oriented based on the chart type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1b855-290">所有 X，Y 圖表類型以外的列，x 軸的帶狀線文字都是以水平方式從左到右的帶狀線的底部導向。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-290">For all X-Y chart types other than Bar, X-axis strip line text is oriented horizontally from left to right on the bottom of the strip line.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1b855-291">橫條圖是垂直方向往右邊帶狀線的 x 軸寬帶線文字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-291">For Bar charts, X-axis strip line text is oriented vertically from top to bottom to the right of the strip line.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="1b855-292">下列程式碼範例示範如何圖表控制項加入至設計介面後，加入臨界值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-292">The following code example demonstrates how to add a threshold line after the chart control has been added to the design surface.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1b855-293">圖表可顯示一系列的所有資料點平均值的計算使用非週期性帶狀線。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1b855-293">The chart uses a non-recurring strip line to show a calculation of the mean of all data points in a series.</span></span>  
  
